<h3 id="calibre-pdf-conversion">Calibre PDF Conversion</h3>
<p>Calibre's biggest strength is PDF handling. While PDF-to-EPUB is never perfect (PDFs are fixed-layout, EPUBs are reflowable), Calibre's heuristic processing does a better job than almost anything else at extracting clean text from PDFs.</p>
<p>Enable <strong>"OCR the input"</strong> in the conversion settings for scanned PDFs, and Calibre will run Tesseract OCR to extract the text layer.</p>
