<p>If you're managing a 2,000-book library and want to standardize everything to EPUB, Calibre's "Add books" + "Convert books" bulk action is the fastest path. The CLI tool <code>ebook-convert</code> lets you script conversions across a whole directory with a one-liner: <code>ebook-convert manuscript.docx manuscript.epub</code>. Power users also rely on the "Recipes" feature to fetch RSS feeds and news sites and deliver them as a fresh EPUB each morning.</p>
